Localization.Name: Valkyrie T-Shirt
Localization.Description: Built for the battlefield, the Valkyrie bravely dives into the kind of danger that other ships avoid. Its ability to deploy ground troops and vehicles swiftly has made it a military favorite for decades. Now popular in the civilian market, this black t-shirt does the Valkyrie justice with a dynamic design across the front and the ship's name on the back.
